## Mode Switching Tabs

![](Engine/Animation/Persona\ModeSelector.gif)(convert:false)

The Persona Toolbar also contains buttons to switch between each of its four modes. These buttons have some functionality in and of themselves that can be useful when trying to track down a particular animation asset. You change Persona modes by simply clicking on the button for the desired mode.

